  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th Level, you learn to reinforce an ally's fortitude with residual Earth Release Chakra.</p><p> When you cast a Ninjutsu with the Earth Release Keyword, you may select one allied creature (excluding yourself) within 60 feet, granting them an aegis.</p><p> The aegis is a thin layer of Earth Release chakra that protects the target.</p><p> Any damage the target takes is reduced by half your Ninjutsu Specialist level.</p><p> This effect ends after the target would take damage of any type.</p><p> You can enhance a creature in this way twice per rest.</p>",
